Explain. Connect the dots for me.

11
00:03:26.740 --> 00:03:28.330 
我亲爱的代表们
My fellow representatives,

12
00:03:27.310 --> 00:03:30.810 
美国众议院 上午八时五十一分

13
00:03:28.370 --> 00:03:31.830 
我的良知驱使我发声反对HR723
my conscience demands that I speak out against HR723,

14
00:03:31.870 --> 00:03:34.290 
那个所谓的"校园健康午餐行动"
the so-called "Healthy School Lunch Act."

15
00:03:34.330 --> 00:03:36.080 
